4Games]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| ''[[NASCAR Heat 4]]''\n| September 13, 2019\n| [[PlayStation 4]], [[Xbox One]], [[Microsoft Windows]]\n| [[Monster Games]], [[704Games]]\n| [[704Games]]\n|}\n\n====Arcade/casual/other====\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\" cellpadding=\"1\" style=\"font-size:85%; text-align:center; width:auto;\"\n|-\n! Title\n! Release date\n! Platform(s)\n! Developer\n! Publisher\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| ''[[3-D Ultra Pinball#3-D Ultra NASCAR Pinball|3-D Ultra NASCAR Pinball]]''\n| 1998\n| [[IBM PC compatible|PC]], [[Macintosh|Mac]]\n| [[Dynamix]]\n| [[Sierra On-Line|Sierra]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| ''Trivial Pursuit: NASCAR''\n| 1999\n| [[IBM PC compatible|PC]]\n| [[Hasbro Interactive]]\n| [[Hasbro Interactive]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| ''[[NASCAR Rumble]]''\n| January 31, 2000\n| [[PlayStation]]\n| [[Visceral Games|EA Redwood Shores]]\n| [[Electronic Arts]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| ''[[NASCAR Arcade]]''\n| 2000\n| [[Arcade game|Arcade]]\n| [[Sega AM3]]/[[Electronic Arts]]\n| [[Sega]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| ''[[NASCAR Racers#Video game|NASCAR Racers]]''\n| 2000\n| [[PlayStation]], [[Game Boy Color]], [[IBM PC compatible|PC]]\n| [[Majesco Entertainment]]\n| [[Majesco Entertainment]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| ''[[EA Sports NASCAR Racing]]''\n| August 3, 2007\n| [[Video arcade|Arcade]]\n| [[EA Tiburon]]\n| [[EA Sports]], [[Global VR]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| ''[[Days of Thunder (video game)|Days of Thunder]]''\n| February 5, 2009\n| [[iPhone]]\n| [[Piranha Games]]\n| [[Freeverse]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| ''[[NASCAR Kart Racing]]''\n| February 10, 2009\n| [[Wii]]\n| [[EA Tiburon]]\n| [[EA Sports BIG|EA Sports Freestyle]]\n|- style=\"text-align:center;\"\n| ''[[Days of Thunder (2011 video game)|Days of Thunder: Arcade]]''\n| February 22, 2011\n| [[PlayStation Network]], [[Xbox Live Arcade]]\n| [[Piranha Games]]\n| [[Paramount Digital Entertainment]]\n|-